Fixed Apple Maps POI search implementation: Corrected search radius range from 1-10 miles to 1-5 miles as specified in task requirements. Updated POISearchManager and all related tests. Complete implementation includes: MKLocalSearch POI discovery, LocationCategory enum (24 categories, excludes food), POILocation model (name/coordinate/category/distance/bearing/prominence), configurable 1-5 mi radius, bearing calculation, periodic re-search on movement. All tests verified and updated.
